document.title: NI 43-101 Technical Report for the Lustdust Project in North America dated October 2012.pdf
document.description: This report, commissioned by Alpha Gold Corporation and prepared by Aurora Geosciences Ltd., provides an interpretation of the known resources and mineralization of the Lustdust property in north-central British Columbia, summarizing historic exploration work and generating recommendations for future exploration programs.
